{"tid":2170325,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《掃毒》導演陳木勝不敵鼻咽癌病逝 終年58歲","createTime":"2020-08-23T07:39:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T07:56:52.000Z","uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5626fdcf72613d378dc1e84c895bfb967e2e8105","tid":2170325,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:39:39.000Z","msg":"香港導演陳木勝今早不幸因鼻咽癌離世，終年58歲，遺下太太及3子女，而其遺孀心情非常悲傷，至今仍未平服。他最後一部作品是執導由甄子丹和謝霆鋒主演的《怒火》，影片於去年底已拍竣，正待排期上映。據知，他於拍攝電影期間已感身體不適，之後去做了身體檢查，不幸驗出已患上鼻咽癌末期，到拍攝完成已無能力做後期，需交由其他人接手工作。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200823/BUUU2MDCJWNSO4AIDP2VYYX7DM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200823%2FBUUU2MDCJWNSO4AIDP2VYYX7DM%2F&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTL4BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=c3d7fe4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200823%2FBUUU2MDCJWNSO4AIDP2VYYX7DM%2F&h=5f063fa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200823/BUUU2MDCJWNSO4AIDP2VYYX7DM/</a>"},{"pid":"817b617f0412134fdecb1e6cc607f27574550e17","tid":2170325,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:41:52.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"1f28adab565205a8aa9073d3afae63e0680f61e6","tid":2170325,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:44:11.000Z","msg":"rip <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n衝鋒隊怒火街頭超好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52dbbe617e7be981c7f72e467f5c28dc7c86b074","tid":2170325,"uid":124382,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:56:52.000Z","msg":"Rest in Peace."}]}